import { Route, Switch, BrowserRouter, Redirect } from "react-router-dom";
import React from 'react';
import { LoginPage, LogoutPage, Helpers, ErrorPage } from 'core';
import { GetUrl } from './utils/generals'
import Constants from './utils/constants'

import './assets/app.css'

import HomePage from "./pages/homePage";
import RegionInfoListPage from './pages/regionInfo/regionInfoListPage'
import RegionInfoAddPage from './pages/regionInfo/regionInfoAddPage'
import RegionInfoEditPage from './pages/regionInfo/regionInfoEditPage'
import PersonInfListPage from './pages/personnelInfo/personInfListPage'
import PersonInfAddPage from './pages/personnelInfo/personInfAddPage'
import PersonInfEditPage from './pages/personnelInfo/personInfEditPage'
import CustomerActivityLevelAddPage from './pages/customerActivityLevel/customerActivityLevelAddPage'
import CustomerActivityLevelEditPage from './pages/customerActivityLevel/customerActivityLevelEditPage'
import CustomerActivityLevelListPage from './pages/customerActivityLevel/customerActivityLevelListPage'
import PrescribedThresholdAddPage from './pages/prescribedThreshold/prescribedThresholdAddPage'
import PrescribedThresholdEditPage from './pages/prescribedThreshold/prescribedThresholdEditPage'
import PrescribedThresholdListPage from './pages/prescribedThreshold/prescribedThresholdListPage'
import ManagementOfSuspiciousTransactionsAndOperationsListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/managementOfSuspiciousTransactionsAndOperationsListPage'
import DistributionOfIndicatorsPage   from './pages/indicators/distributionOfIndicatorsPage';
import IndicatorsResultPage   from './pages/indicators/indicatorsResultPage';
import ReceiveInvoiceListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/receiveInvoiceListPage';
import ReceiveSTRListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/receiveSTRListPage';
import ReceiveCTRListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/receiveCTRListPage';
import CreateSTRPrimaryListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/createSTRPrimaryListPage';
import TabPage from "./pages/additionalReview/tabPage";
import PersonBillingListPage from './pages/doubtfulEquations/personBillingListPage'

// Report Pages
import RequestBillingAddPage from './pages/report/billings/requestBillingAddPage'
import RequestBillingListPage from './pages/report/billings/requestBillingListPage'

const NoAccessMsg = "شما به این بخش دسترسی ندارید و یا زمان نشت شما به پایان رسیده است";
const NoAccessTitle = "عدم دسترسی";

const AppWrapper = () => {
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>
      <Switch>
        <Route path={ GetUrl("login") } render={(props) => <LoginPage {...props} /> } />
        <Route path="/logout" render={(props) => <LogoutPage {...props} />} />
        <Route exact path='/'
          render={(props) => {
            if (Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated()) {
              if (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin)
                  || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)) {
                if (props.location.search.indexOf("?url=") > -1)
                  return <Redirect to={decodeURIComponent(props.location.search.substring("?url=".length))} />
                return <HomePage {...props} />;
              } else {
                return <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } />
              }
            }
            else {
              if (props.location.search.indexOf("?url=") > -1) {
                const r = decodeURIComponent(props.location.search.substring("?url=".length));
                sessionStorage.setItem('redirectUrl', r);
              }
              return <Redirect to={ GetUrl('login') } {...props} />
            }
          }} />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("regionInfoListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <RegionInfoListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("regionInfoAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <RegionInfoAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
            
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("regionInfoEditPage/:regionInfoId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <RegionInfoEditPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("personInfListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PersonInfListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("personInfAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PersonInfAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("personInfEditPage/:personInfId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PersonInfEditPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("customerActivityLevelListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <CustomerActivityLevelListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("customerActivityLevelAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <CustomerActivityLevelAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("customerActivityLevelEditPage/:customerActivityLevelId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <CustomerActivityLevelEditPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("prescribedThresholdListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PrescribedThresholdListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("prescribedThresholdAddPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PrescribedThresholdAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("prescribedThresholdEditPage/:prescribedThresholdId") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PrescribedThresholdEditPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("managementOfSuspiciousTransactionsAndOperationsListPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <ManagementOfSuspiciousTransactionsAndOperationsListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("distributionOfIndicatorsPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <DistributionOfIndicatorsPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />
        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("indicatorsResultPage") }
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <IndicatorsResultPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("receiveInvoiceListPage/:identifierCode")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <ReceiveInvoiceListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("receiveSTRListPage/:identifierCode")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <ReceiveSTRListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("receiveCTRListPage/:identifierCode")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <ReceiveCTRListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("createSTRPrimaryListPage/:nationalNumber")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <CreateSTRPrimaryListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("additionalReviewPage/:nationalNumber")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <TabPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("requestBillingAddPage")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <RequestBillingAddPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("requestBillingListPage")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <RequestBillingListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("personBillingListPage/:requestId")}
          render={(props) =>
            Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin))
            ? <PersonBillingListPage {...props} />
            : <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> } />

        <Route
          exact
          path={ GetUrl("downlaodPersonBillings/:requestId") }
          render={(props) =>
            {
              if(Helpers.IsUserAuthenticated() && (Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SuperAdmin) || Helpers.IsInRole(Constants.Roles.SystemAdmin)))
              {
                props.history.goBack();
                window.open(`/api/amls/PersonBilling/DownloadPersonBillings/${props.match.params.requestId}`, '_target')
              }
              else
                <ErrorPage title={ NoAccessTitle } description={ NoAccessMsg } /> }
            } />

        <Route render={(props) => <ErrorPage {...props} title="صفحه مورد نظر شما در سامانه یافت نشد"
          description="صفحه مورد نظر شما در سامانه حذف شده است یا احتمالا شما مجوز لازم جهت دسترسی به صفحه مذکور را ندارید" />} />
      </Switch>
    </BrowserRouter>
  );
};

export default AppWrapper;
